snippet.title: ShirleyCobain
snippet.description:
Videos of Alice in Chains, Heath Ledger, River Phoenix, Keanu Reeves, Tom Hardy, Marion Cotillard, Matthias Schoenaerts and Michael Fassbender.

If you speak French or Flemish/Dutch and would like to help with the English subtitles for some of my videos, leave me a message.

Subscribe to my channel / Se inscreva no canal!
https://www.youtube.com/user/ShirleyCobain?sub_confirmation=1

Follow me on Twitter!
https://twitter.com/ShirleyCobain
